<p class="ayah 54-35" id="35" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نِّعْمَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(As) a favor</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِندِنَا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Us.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَذَٲلِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Thus</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَجْزِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We reward</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(one) who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَكَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) grateful.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>35<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 54-36" id="36" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَقَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And certainly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنذَرَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">he warned them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَطْشَتَنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Our seizure,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَتَمَارَوْاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but they disputed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلنُّذُرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the warnings.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>36<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
