<p class="ayah 54-38" id="38" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَقَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And certainly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">صَبَّحَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">seized them in the morning</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بُكْرَةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">early</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّسْتَقِرٌّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">abiding.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>38<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 54-39" id="39" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَذُوقُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So taste</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">My punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَنُذُرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and My warnings.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>39<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 54-40" id="40" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَقَدْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And certainly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَسَّرْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We have made easy</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقُرْءَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Quran</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِلذِّكْرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for remembrance,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَهَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so is (there)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّدَّكِرٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who will receive admonition?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>40<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
