<p class="ayah 54-42" id="42" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَذَّبُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">They denied</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِـَٔـايَـٰتِنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Our Signs,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلِّهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">all of them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأَخَذْنَـٰهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so We seized them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَخْذَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(with) a seizure</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَزِيزٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) All-Mighty,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّقْتَدِرٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) Powerful One.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>42<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 54-43" id="43" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَكُفَّارُكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Are your disbelievers,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَيْرٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">better</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">than</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوْلَـٰٓئِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَرَآءَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) an exemption</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلزُّبُرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Scriptures?</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>43<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 54-44" id="44" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَقُولُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(do) they say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَحْنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`We</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَمِيعٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) an assembly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّنتَصِرٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">helping (each other)?`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>44<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 54-45" id="45" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَيُهْزَمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Soon will be defeated</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْجَمْعُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(their) assembly,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيُوَلُّونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and they will turn</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلدُّبُرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(their) backs.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>45<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
