<p class="ayah 54-48" id="48" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(The) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُسْحَبُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they will be dragged</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">into</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّارِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Fire</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وُجُوهِهِمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their faces,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذُوقُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Taste</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَسَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) touch</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَقَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Hell.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>48<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 54-49" id="49" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, [We]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">every</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَىْءٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">thing</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَلَقْنَـٰهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We created it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِقَدَرٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by a measure.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>49<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 54-50" id="50" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْرُنَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) Our Command</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٲحِدَةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">one,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَلَمْحِۭ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">like the twinkling</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْبَصَرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the eye.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>50<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
